      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Note that this merely returns the integer part of the Double, so for 13.666667 or even 13.9, you&#39;ll get 13, not 14. If you want the <i>nearest</i> integer, refer to my answer: <a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/a/24816336/1450294\">stackoverflow.com/a/24816336/1450294</a>"
    }, {
