      "post_id" : 20373065,
      "comment_id" : 41788951,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Don&#39;t use <code>new Integer(int)</code>, instead use <code>Integer.valueOf(int)</code> , which has a cache for small integers, such as this one."
    } ],
    "owner" : {
