    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<pre><code>Double d = 100.00;\nInteger i = d.intValue();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>One should also add that it works with autoboxing.</p>\n\n<p>Otherwise, you get an int (primitive) and then can get an Integer from there:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Integer i = new Integer(d.intValue());\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
